They must be somewhere
else in the building.

47:26.417 --> 47:27.583
It's all clear.

47:27.583 --> 47:29.250
Okay.

47:29.250 --> 47:32.625
Camera panning... off.

47:32.625 --> 47:34.875
( computer beeps  )

47:46.917 --> 47:48.375
( Max growls playfully  )

47:48.375 --> 47:51.000
No. Max. No.

47:51.000 --> 47:52.250
( whirring  )

47:54.291 --> 47:55.083
Go back, Maddy.

47:59.542 --> 48:01.500
Austin?

48:01.500 --> 48:03.792
( Max laughing  )
Max, no!
Not the camera.

48:03.792 --> 48:04.750
( Max laughing  )
This is not a toy.

48:04.750 --> 48:05.834
No, no, not a toy.

48:05.834 --> 48:07.708
Austin!

48:07.708 --> 48:09.834
Max...!

48:09.834 --> 48:11.625
Okay, I got it.

48:11.625 --> 48:13.125
( computer beeps  )
Go.

48:18.500 --> 48:20.792
( punching keypad  )
How do you know the dogs

48:20.792 --> 48:21.959
aren't gonna be waiting
on the other side

48:21.959 --> 48:23.333
of that door?

48:23.333 --> 48:24.375
I don't.

48:24.375 --> 48:25.333
But I guess we find out.

48:35.625 --> 48:37.458
( dogs panting  )

48:40.583 --> 48:42.333
( gasps  )

48:44.917 --> 48:47.458
Whoa, that's high.

48:52.917 --> 48:55.291
Good-bye, my babies.

48:55.291 --> 48:56.291
Just don't look down.

48:56.291 --> 48:57.417
You'll be fine.

48:57.417 --> 48:59.667
What is this?

48:59.667 --> 49:00.917
Another door.

49:00.917 --> 49:02.542
How do you open
this one?

49:02.542 --> 49:06.333
Open sesame!

49:06.333 --> 49:07.792
This one doesn't
even have

49:07.792 --> 49:10.125
any numbers on it.

49:11.750 --> 49:13.792
GUS:
Whoa, cool!

49:16.875 --> 49:19.166
( computer beeping  )

49:21.375 --> 49:23.125
( beeping continues  )

49:23.125 --> 49:25.041
Mr. Ferr...
uh, Lieutenant Ferrell?

49:25.041 --> 49:26.375
CHAD ( over radio  ):
Breaker, breaker.

49:26.375 --> 49:27.500
What?
I saw something
in Sector Five.

49:27.500 --> 49:29.625
All right. I'll be right up.

49:29.625 --> 49:31.708
FERRELL ( over radio  ):
Don't get your panties in a wad.

49:34.750 --> 49:37.000
( grunts  )

49:37.000 --> 49:38.875
( startled shout  )

49:40.875 --> 49:41.917
( keypad blips  )

49:45.750 --> 49:47.333
( keypad blips  )

49:50.000 --> 49:51.500
( door rumbling  )

49:57.667 --> 49:59.625
Whoa.

49:59.625 --> 50:02.375
Maddy,
we are so grounded.

50:03.792 --> 50:06.333
Say good-bye to my Xbox,

50:06.333 --> 50:09.625
my iPod, my go-cart.

50:09.625 --> 50:11.750
I'm gonna have
to take out the trash,

50:11.750 --> 50:13.750
do the dishes,

50:13.750 --> 50:16.583
massage Grandma's cold feet.

50:17.917 --> 50:19.500
( sighs  )

50:19.500 --> 50:20.834
FERRELL:
What?

50:20.834 --> 50:23.125
I-I saw something
in Sector Five.

50:25.542 --> 50:27.333
In that... region.

50:27.333 --> 50:28.625
Sector Five, huh?

50:28.625 --> 50:29.875
Mm-hmm.

50:29.875 --> 50:33.834
I was just in Sector Five.

50:33.834 --> 50:36.875
That was me, you idiot!

50:36.875 --> 50:38.875
( sighs  )

50:38.875 --> 50:41.208
Chad, did I ever tell you
a story

50:41.208 --> 50:44.917
about the boy who cried
Sector Five one too many times?

50:44.917 --> 50:46.667
Huh?

50:46.667 --> 50:49.583
Holy...

50:49.583 --> 50:51.834
That's where they keep
all the money?

50:51.834 --> 50:54.542
Thanks a lot, Mom.

50:54.542 --> 50:56.542
HARTMANN:
And this

50:56.542 --> 50:57.542
is Mr. Brisbane's office.

50:57.542 --> 50:59.000
Just look at that view.

50:59.000 --> 50:59.750
Someone's coming.
Get down.

50:59.750 --> 51:01.458
Hold on.

51:04.125 --> 51:06.875
So, I finally have
you all to myself.

51:06.875 --> 51:08.875
Well, I like to come up
to Mr. Brisbane's office

51:08.875 --> 51:10.959
when I know he's not here!

51:10.959 --> 51:13.208
GUS:
Maddy, it's way too high
to climb to the safe.

51:13.208 --> 51:14.875
There's gotta be some way
to bring it down.

51:14.875 --> 51:17.625
Then come help me look.

51:17.625 --> 51:19.000
Gus!

51:19.000 --> 51:20.458
( echoing  ):
Gus! Gus!

51:20.458 --> 51:22.417
Gus, come help me!

51:25.458 --> 51:26.834
( blips  )

51:26.834 --> 51:30.000
( rumbling  )

51:39.583 --> 51:42.208
Holy...

51:45.500 --> 51:46.625
You know "The Planet
of the Apes"?

51:46.625 --> 51:48.000
Mm-hmm.

51:48.000 --> 51:50.083
Well, I was in that movie.

51:50.083 --> 51:51.667
I love that movie!

51:53.750 --> 51:55.708
( kissing  )

51:57.667 --> 52:01.250
Whoa, that's fresh.

52:01.250 --> 52:03.083
What'd you do?
I don't know.

52:03.083 --> 52:04.125
I just stepped
on this dude's eye.

52:06.500 --> 52:08.667
These numbers match the ones
all over the wall.

52:08.667 --> 52:09.917
( blips twice  )

52:09.917 --> 52:11.875
They're safety deposit boxes.

52:11.875 --> 52:12.875
( blip  )

52:15.875 --> 52:17.375
I bet you if we press one...

52:20.708 --> 52:21.542
Whoa.

52:27.250 --> 52:29.041
( sighs  )

52:30.917 --> 52:33.041
My mom's gonna kill me.

52:33.041 --> 52:35.750
MADDY:
Retract 3-2-1-2.

52:35.750 --> 52:36.917
( blipping  )

52:41.041 --> 52:43.834
Hit 2-3-5-7.

52:43.834 --> 52:45.417
( blip, drawer opens  )

52:47.041 --> 52:48.667
( woman laughs  )

52:48.667 --> 52:49.708
Mama.

52:49.708 --> 52:51.792
M...

52:51.792 --> 52:53.834
That's right.

52:53.834 --> 52:54.917
Come to mama.

52:54.917 --> 52:55.792
( woman laughs  )

52:55.792 --> 52:57.125
Oh, yes!

52:57.125 --> 52:58.417
( knocking on door  )

53:00.750 --> 53:02.792
( screams  )

53:02.792 --> 53:05.792
Mr. Hart...?!
( gasps  )

53:05.792 --> 53:08.291
And that concludes our tour
of the ninth floor.

53:08.291 --> 53:10.291
Now, let's get you
back to the party.

53:16.166 --> 53:17.583
Stockholders.
( whimpers  )

53:20.792 --> 53:23.750
( grunting and panting  )

53:23.750 --> 53:25.125
( drawer opening  )

53:28.750 --> 53:31.417
This is going to work.

53:31.417 --> 53:33.625
Maddy, you can't climb this.
It's too dangerous.

53:33.625 --> 53:34.959
You'll never make it.

53:34.959 --> 53:37.125
I'm doing it.

53:37.125 --> 53:38.750
Austin, you've got to hack
into the main whatever

53:38.750 --> 53:40.250
and find some way
to bring down the safe.

53:40.250 --> 53:41.542
Maddy's going to kill herself.

53:41.542 --> 53:43.000
AUSTIN ( over radio  ):
Check. Searching now.

53:43.000 --> 53:44.708
Gus, I love you.

53:44.708 --> 53:46.792
Now, do what I say.

53:46.792 --> 53:49.875
Okay?

53:49.875 --> 53:50.959
Five-three-four-four.

53:50.959 --> 53:52.959
( blows  )

53:52.959 --> 53:54.125
( beeps  )

53:54.125 --> 53:55.625
( drawer opening  )

53:57.291 --> 53:59.125
AUSTIN:
I'm searching for

53:59.125 --> 54:00.792
the hydraulic controls
for the safe, but...

54:00.792 --> 54:01.875
( beeping  )

54:01.875 --> 54:03.708
You guys, I can't find anything.

54:03.708 --> 54:05.291
AUSTIN:
What's going on in there?

54:05.291 --> 54:06.875
MADDY:
Two-two-four-four.

54:06.875 --> 54:08.125
You don't want
to know, dude.

54:08.125 --> 54:09.125
AUSTIN:
I do want to know.

54:09.125 --> 54:11.041
What's next?

54:11.041 --> 54:12.959
Four-two-three-one.

54:12.959 --> 54:14.000
( grunting  )

54:15.792 --> 54:17.792
Gus!

54:17.792 --> 54:19.000
( whispers  ):
Sorry.

54:19.000 --> 54:20.834
You're killing me
here, dude. Focus.

54:20.834 --> 54:23.375
Retract four-two-
three-two.

54:25.000 --> 54:26.375
( gasps  )

54:26.375 --> 54:27.875
( clinking glass  )

54:27.875 --> 54:29.333
Good evening, everyone.
How are you?

54:29.333 --> 54:30.750
Having a wonderful time,
are we?

54:30.750 --> 54:33.000
Terrific.

54:33.000 --> 54:34.917
To our generous
Board of Directors,

54:34.917 --> 54:37.166
here's to the only type
of success

54:37.166 --> 54:38.875
that really
matters--

54:38.875 --> 54:40.834
financial!

54:40.834 --> 54:42.125
( laughs  )

54:43.834 --> 54:45.291
Cheers!

54:45.291 --> 54:47.959
MADDY:
Okay, Gus, last one.

54:47.959 --> 54:49.834
Five-three-four-three.

54:49.834 --> 54:51.208
( drawer opens  )

54:54.250 --> 54:56.083
COMPUTER:
Security breach.

54:56.083 --> 54:57.959
Security breach.

54:57.959 --> 54:59.166
And now...

54:59.166 --> 55:00.291
( laughs  )

55:00.291 --> 55:02.291
( alarm sounding  )

55:02.291 --> 55:03.667
( murmuring  )

55:03.667 --> 55:04.834
COMPUTER:
Security breach.

55:04.834 --> 55:07.375
Security breach.

55:07.375 --> 55:09.250
Do something.

55:10.708 --> 55:11.834
Do something now.

55:13.291 --> 55:15.083
Anything.

55:16.792 --> 55:18.250
Oh, shoot. Tape.

55:18.250 --> 55:20.375
Austin, the tape. Run the tape!

55:20.375 --> 55:22.792
( gasps  ):
Okay.

55:22.792 --> 55:23.917
( beeps  )

55:23.917 --> 55:28.208
( grunting, sniffing  )

55:31.708 --> 55:33.083
FERRELL:
Mr. Hartmann,

55:33.083 --> 55:34.208
the alarm has sounded.

55:34.208 --> 55:36.041
Take it easy.

55:36.041 --> 55:37.667
It's only me.

55:37.667 --> 55:39.375
Just turn the alarm off.

55:39.375 --> 55:41.458
I should
let out the dogs.

55:41.458 --> 55:42.708
Calm down, princess.
It's fine.

55:42.708 --> 55:45.166
It's... really.

55:45.166 --> 55:47.166
No, nothing to worry about.

55:47.166 --> 55:49.917
It's... I'm right here.

55:49.917 --> 55:52.667
Just turn off the alarm.

55:52.667 --> 55:53.583
Uh, should I, uh...

55:55.083 --> 55:57.458
Kill the alarm.

55:59.166 --> 56:01.875
( alarm stops  )

56:01.875 --> 56:04.375
( relieved sigh  )

56:04.375 --> 56:06.083
Well!

56:06.083 --> 56:07.875
It seems that our
security system works.

56:07.875 --> 56:09.041
( laughing  )

56:09.041 --> 56:11.041
Yes.

56:11.041 --> 56:12.875
It's just a false alarm,
everyone, so why don't

56:12.875 --> 56:15.834
we all just relax and enjoy
this wonderful party,

56:15.834 --> 56:17.083
what do you
say?Sure.

56:17.083 --> 56:18.875
Wonderful. Please.

56:18.875 --> 56:20.250
( applause  )

56:20.250 --> 56:21.500
Something's
going on here.

56:21.500 --> 56:24.250
I'm going to find out
what it is.

56:24.250 --> 56:25.417
( yelling  )

56:25.417 --> 56:26.959
The monitor!

56:32.959 --> 56:36.792
( breathing deeply  )

56:36.792 --> 56:38.500
I can do this.

56:44.375 --> 56:48.166
( clinking  )

56:48.166 --> 56:49.291
Maddy, be careful.

56:56.125 --> 56:57.291
( grunts  )

57:00.500 --> 57:03.792
( clinking  )

57:03.792 --> 57:05.166
Maddy, my parents
grounded me for a week

57:05.166 --> 57:07.125
when I left my bike outside.

57:07.125 --> 57:09.041
Imagine what they'll do
if they catch us now.

57:12.166 --> 57:13.500
We'll figure out
a different way.

57:13.500 --> 57:14.542
It's too dangerous.

57:16.500 --> 57:17.917
She's not listening to me.

57:17.917 --> 57:19.500
She clearly doesn't understand.

57:19.500 --> 57:21.333
She's climbing up
this stupid wall and...

57:21.333 --> 57:23.041
Austin, maybe
she'd listen to you.

57:23.041 --> 57:25.083
AUSTIN ( over radio  ):
That would be a first.

57:25.083 --> 57:26.250
GUS:
I wonder if you can

57:26.250 --> 57:27.542
finish the eighth grade
in prison.

57:31.375 --> 57:33.208
Oh, wait-- if we're in jail,

57:33.208 --> 57:35.041
our parents
can't ground us, right?

57:42.500 --> 57:45.291
( gasping  )

57:45.291 --> 57:47.041
No...

57:49.583 --> 57:52.083
Come on, this cannot
be happening.

57:52.083 --> 57:54.041
The cam's stuck.

57:54.041 --> 57:55.375
It's stuck.

57:57.667 --> 57:59.208
TOM'S VOICE:
20 feet from the summit,

57:59.208 --> 58:01.375
my gear stuck.

58:01.375 --> 58:03.375
There was this perfect crack

58:03.375 --> 58:05.375
running all the way
up to the top.

58:09.917 --> 58:11.583
He free-climbed it.

58:20.291 --> 58:22.834
( grunts  )

58:22.834 --> 58:27.500
Maddy, are you
free-climbing this?!

58:27.500 --> 58:29.291
Maddy, no!

58:32.208 --> 58:35.625
( grunting  )

58:35.625 --> 58:37.041
Maddy, we never
even got to kiss.

58:45.291 --> 58:48.875
( grunting  )

58:53.959 --> 58:57.083
( grunting, panting  )

59:03.291 --> 59:05.250
( gasps  )

59:05.250 --> 59:08.083
( grunting  )

59:10.375 --> 59:12.125
( gasping  )

59:18.125 --> 59:19.458
( metal creaking  )

59:19.458 --> 59:21.291
( Maddy grunting  )

59:21.291 --> 59:23.458
( panting  )

59:23.458 --> 59:26.000
( metal creaking  )

59:31.458 --> 59:32.458
( grunting  )

59:34.291 --> 59:35.667
( grunting  )

59:45.000 --> 59:48.417
( panting  )

59:48.417 --> 59:49.667
She's looking down.

59:49.667 --> 59:51.250
She's looking down!

59:51.250 --> 59:52.500
Tell her not to!

59:52.500 --> 59:54.375
Oh, why did I look down?

59:54.375 --> 59:55.458
That's high.

59:55.458 --> 59:57.208
Maddy, don't look down!

59:59.333 --> 01:00:01.083
Oh, that's high.

01:00:01.083 --> 01:00:02.291
It's not high.

01:00:02.291 --> 01:00:03.583
I can do it.

01:00:03.583 --> 01:00:06.500
( breathes deeply  )

01:00:06.500 --> 01:00:07.458
Gus looks like an ant.

01:00:07.458 --> 01:00:08.500
( grunts  )

01:00:08.500 --> 01:00:09.959
Okay...

01:00:13.041 --> 01:00:14.542
( grunts  )

01:00:16.166 --> 01:00:19.041
Okay...

01:00:19.041 --> 01:00:21.166
One...

01:00:21.166 --> 01:00:22.625
Two...

01:00:25.083 --> 01:00:26.708
...Two and a half...

01:00:29.542 --> 01:00:31.083
Maddy, no!

01:00:31.083 --> 01:00:32.625
...Three!

01:00:32.625 --> 01:00:34.542
( grunts  )

01:00:34.542 --> 01:00:35.083
( gasps  )
Whoa!

01:00:37.417 --> 01:00:38.750
Maddy!
( grunts  )

01:00:41.708 --> 01:00:43.041
Gus?
( panting  )

01:00:45.500 --> 01:00:47.208
( beeping  )

01:00:47.208 --> 01:00:48.542
Oh, no.

01:00:48.542 --> 01:00:50.875
She set off a timer, Gus.

01:00:50.875 --> 01:00:52.125
She has two minutes
to enter the code

01:00:52.125 --> 01:00:53.375
before the alarm goes off.

01:00:53.375 --> 01:00:54.542
Maddy, you've
triggered the timer.

01:00:54.542 --> 01:00:55.625
You've got to reach the keypad.

01:00:55.625 --> 01:00:57.208
( beeping  )

01:01:00.500 --> 01:01:02.542
( straining  )

01:01:10.625 --> 01:01:12.041
( softly  ):
Okay, Wolfgang.

01:01:15.667 --> 01:01:18.375
( beeping  )

01:01:18.375 --> 01:01:21.583
D-E-N-I-R-O.

01:01:21.583 --> 01:01:22.583
( sustained beep  )

01:01:22.583 --> 01:01:24.250
COMPUTER:
Access denied.

01:01:24.250 --> 01:01:25.792
Oh, no!

01:01:25.792 --> 01:01:28.166
De Niro's
not the code?!

01:01:28.166 --> 01:01:29.500
I can't
believe it.

01:01:29.500 --> 01:01:31.291
( beeping  )

01:01:31.291 --> 01:01:33.208
I can't break
the access code, Maddy.

01:01:33.208 --> 01:01:34.208
( beeping  )

01:01:34.208 --> 01:01:36.166
Your mom designed

01:01:36.166 --> 01:01:37.625
the safe, so the code
must be something she chose.

01:01:37.625 --> 01:01:40.166
What could it be?

01:01:40.166 --> 01:01:41.583
What did you use?

01:01:43.625 --> 01:01:45.083
Maxwell.

01:01:45.083 --> 01:01:48.417
( keypad beeping  )

01:01:48.417 --> 01:01:50.166
( sustained beep  )

01:01:50.166 --> 01:01:51.250
COMPUTER:
Access denied.

01:01:51.250 --> 01:01:53.208
No!

01:01:53.208 --> 01:01:54.291
Come on, Maddy.

01:01:54.291 --> 01:01:56.458
Think!

01:01:56.458 --> 01:01:59.291
Come on, Maddy.

01:01:59.291 --> 01:02:00.708
Come on.

01:02:00.708 --> 01:02:02.625
( softly  ):
Come on.

01:02:02.625 --> 01:02:04.625
Oh, what could it be?

01:02:04.625 --> 01:02:07.125
Mom, what did you use?

01:02:09.250 --> 01:02:11.333
Dad.

01:02:11.333 --> 01:02:12.250
( grunts  )

01:02:14.458 --> 01:02:16.625
( keypad beeping  )

01:02:16.625 --> 01:02:18.291
( sustained beep  )

01:02:18.291 --> 01:02:20.458
COMPUTER:
Access denied.

01:02:20.458 --> 01:02:23.959
( breath quivering  )

01:02:23.959 --> 01:02:26.333
MOLLY'S VOICE:
I do think about you, Madeline.

01:02:26.333 --> 01:02:27.708
Every day.

01:02:27.708 --> 01:02:29.333
All the time.

01:02:32.542 --> 01:02:35.625
( panting  )

01:02:39.667 --> 01:02:43.792
( beeping  )

01:02:43.792 --> 01:02:45.834
Madeline.

01:02:45.834 --> 01:02:47.625
COMPUTER:
Access code accepted.

01:02:47.625 --> 01:02:49.625
( soft chuckle  )

01:02:49.625 --> 01:02:51.625
( door rumbling  )

01:02:55.583 --> 01:02:58.333
( clinking  )

01:03:05.250 --> 01:03:07.041
She used my name!

01:03:07.041 --> 01:03:09.041
My name as the code!
( excited grunt  )

01:03:09.041 --> 01:03:10.625
In your face,
Harderbach Financial!

01:03:10.625 --> 01:03:11.834
AUSTIN ( over radio  ):
Gus?

01:03:11.834 --> 01:03:13.750
What happened?

01:03:13.750 --> 01:03:14.708
GUS:
She made it. She's in the safe.

01:03:19.500 --> 01:03:20.375
Is the money there?

01:03:20.375 --> 01:03:21.583
Hey, Gus.

01:03:21.583 --> 01:03:23.417
250 grand coming at ya.

01:03:25.708 --> 01:03:26.750
( whooshes  )

01:03:28.291 --> 01:03:28.917
Nope.

01:03:30.542 --> 01:03:32.542
It's down here.

01:03:32.542 --> 01:03:34.375
Good job, Max.

01:03:41.959 --> 01:03:43.750
AUSTIN ( over radio  ):
All right.

01:03:43.750 --> 01:03:45.917
I'll meet you guys at the carts.

01:03:45.917 --> 01:03:47.375
Austin, we're
on the move.

01:03:47.375 --> 01:03:50.166
COMPUTER:
Exit code requested.

01:03:50.166 --> 01:03:54.583
